title: You're Not Allowed To Look At These Bugs

media:group.media:title: You're Not Allowed To Look At These Bugs
media:group.media:description:
This video is a re-upload. Youtube initially age-restricted and demonetized the original upload within the first day of its publication, effectively preventing any additional viewers from discovering it. I have since replaced any visuals I believe Youtube may have deemed worthy reasons to block the video.

Ironic that my video talking about censorship gets censored.
